menu "breadboard: bb_temp"

config BB_TEMP_AUTOREGISTER
    bool "Auto-register /api/health \"temp\" section via bb_init"
    default n
    help
        When enabled, bb_temp self-registers the "temp" health section through
        bb_init (regular tier, order 1 — after bb_health PRE_HTTP init).
        Consumers that call bb_temp_register_info() manually must leave this
        disabled; enabling both double-registers the section. Default n
        preserves backward-compatible manual-register behavior.

        To switch to auto-register: enable this option and remove the
        bb_temp_register_info() call from app_main / bringup code.

endmenu
